OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and showers, some
OL,6,Fof these wintry with hail and hill
OL,7,Fsnow possible, particularly in the
OL,8,Fnorth. Showers prolonged at first
OL,9,Facross part of England and Wales with
OL,10,Fthe odd rumble of thunder. Feeling
OL,11,Fcold in the wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing from the west,
OL,14,Fleaving clear spells and a fairly
OL,15,Fwidespread frost developing across
OL,16,Fmuch of England and Wales. Turning wet
OL,17,Fand windy across the north west later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
