OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA bright but chilly start
OL,6,Facross the southeast, cloud and rain
OL,7,Falready across the northwest will
OL,8,Fspread to all areas during the day.
OL,9,FFeeling cold with strong gusty winds.
